    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1951-12-22T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1951-12-22T00:00:00-05:00" n="294"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d294">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">320/12–2251: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Acting Chairman of the United States Delegation to the
                        General Assembly</hi> (<persName type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Roosevelt</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#left">
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">priority</hi>
                    </seg>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Paris</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1951-12-22">December 22,
                            1951</date>.<lb/>[Received December 22—4:22 p. m.]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>
                    <gloss target="#t_Delga1">Delga</gloss> 794. Re <gloss target="#t_SC1"
                        >SC</gloss> [meeting] membership. Following is text of draft resolution
                    submitted ISC on Dec 19.</p>
                <p>Draft resolution concerning the admission of new members, submitted by the <gloss
                        target="#t_del1">del</gloss> Union Socialist Republics at the 569th meeting
                    of the Council on 19 December 1951:</p>
                <quote rend="blockquote">
                    <p>
                        <hi rend="italic">“The <gloss target="#t_SC1">SC</gloss>
                        </hi>,</p>
                    <p>“<hi rend="italic">Having examined</hi> the applications of Albania, the
                        Mongolian People’s Republic, Bulgaria, Romania, Hungary, Finland, Italy,
                        Portugal, Ireland, The Hashemite Kingdom of Jordan, Austria, Ceylon and
                        Nepal for admission to membership of the <gloss target="#t_UN1"
                        >UN</gloss>.</p>
                    <p>“<hi rend="italic">Recommends</hi> the <gloss target="#t_GA1">GA</gloss> to
                        admit those states to membership of the <gloss target="#t_UN1"
                        >UN</gloss>.”</p>
                </quote>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Roosevelt</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
